Summary: I was taking a picture of a sunset.
divs: Sighting DetailsI stopped to take a picture of Laramie Peak at sunset.I was facing West about 2 miles East of Interstate 25.As you can see ,it is a nice sunset.I don't know what the objects in the left hand side of the photo are.I was hoping you could tell me.This picture was shot with a 700C Olympus Digital Camera.
